The 14th edition of the Headies (Headies 2020) ushered us not only into the celebration of outstanding artistes in the Nigerian music industry in the past year but into the fashion trend on the red carpet for the year 2021. Hosts- Bovi and Nancy Isime Fireboy DML takes the lead with nine nominations while Davido and Wurld follow closely with seven nominations each. Burna Boy, who is also the reigning Artiste of the Year, secured six nominations. Read More: Live Update: All The Winners At The Headies 2020 On the heels of the pandemic, we saw celebrities who came to show off and show out. Here are some of the invitees that caught our attention. 